OL,3,CChief Fire Officer of Mid and Wales
OL,4,CFire Service to step down
OL,6,FThe Chief Fire Officer at Mid and West
OL,7,FWales Fire Service will step down this
OL,8,Fyear, ITV Cymru Wales understands.
OL,10,FRoger Thomas has worked within the
OL,11,Fforce for 29-years, taking on the post
OL,12,Fas Chief Fire Officer in April 2022.
OL,13,FHe is expected to retire in October.
OL,15,FMr Thomas was recognised in the King's
OL,16,FBirthday Honours earlier this month
OL,17,Ffor his commitment to the force.
