OL,3,CChief Fire Officer of Mid and Wales
OL,4,CFire Service to step down
OL,6,FThe news of his retirement comes after
OL,7,Fan independent investigation into
OL,8,Fculture at Mid and West Wales Fire
OL,9,FService published in February saw one
OL,10,Fparticipant brand the force an
OL,11,F"operational boys club".
OL,13,FNearly half (47%) of people who
OL,14,Fresponded to the survey reported
OL,15,Fpersonal experiences with bullying and
OL,16,Fharassment in the service since June
OL,17,F2021, and over half (54%) had
OL,18,Fwitnessed such behaviours, the report
OL,19,Ffound.
