OL,3,CChief Fire Officer of Mid and Wales
OL,4,CFire Service to step down
OL,6,F10% of female survey respondents
OL,7,Freported experiencing sexual
OL,8,Fharassment, with the report suggesting
OL,9,Fsexual assault or harassment continues
OL,10,Fto go largely underreported.
OL,12,FResponding to the independent
OL,13,Finvestigation into workplace culture
OL,14,Fat the time, Mr Thomas said he
OL,15,Fapologises "unreservedly" to
OL,16,Fcolleagues who have been subject to
OL,17,F"bullying, harassment or
OL,18,Fdiscrimination in any form."
