OL,3,CChief Fire Officer of Mid and Wales
OL,4,CFire Service to step down
OL,6,FHe added, "This is wholly unacceptable
OL,7,Fand does not align with the values and
OL,8,Fbehaviours that we espouse or endorse
OL,9,Fas a Service.
OL,11,F"Secondly, I accept the findings and
OL,12,Frecommendations within the review
OL,13,Fwhich support my ambition to improve
OL,14,Fthe culture of our Service, which was
OL,15,Fone of my key aims when I was
OL,16,Fappointed as Chief Fire Officer."
